## Lumen UI React — usage rules

### Setup Requirements

- Import components from `@ledgerhq/lumen-ui-react`
- Import icons from `@ledgerhq/lumen-ui-react/symbols` (not from main package)
- Import design tokens/presets from `@ledgerhq/lumen-design-core`
- Font: Lumen typography sets `font-family: Inter`. The sample app already loads
  Inter via react-ui's `StyleProvider` (`fontsPath="/fonts"`).
- Tailwind config MUST include Lumen in `content`:
  `'./node_modules/@ledgerhq/lumen-ui-react/dist/lib/**/*.{js,ts,jsx,tsx}'`
- Always use a preset: `ledgerLivePreset`, `enterprisePreset` or `websitesPreset`.

### Peer Dependencies

- Button requires `@radix-ui/react-slot`
- Checkbox requires `@radix-ui/react-checkbox`
- Switch requires `@radix-ui/react-switch`
- Dialog requires `@radix-ui/react-dialog`
- Tooltip requires `@radix-ui/react-tooltip`
- Select requires `@base-ui/react/combobox`

### Design Tokens

**Typography** — do NOT use Tailwind typography utilities (`font-bold`, `text-sm`, …).
Use Lumen utilities: `responsive-display-1..4`, `heading-0..5` (+ `-semi-bold`),
`body-1..4` (+ `-semi-bold`).

**Colors** — do NOT use Tailwind's default palette (`text-gray-500`, `bg-blue-600`).
Use Lumen semantic tokens (auto-adapt to light/dark):
- Backgrounds: `bg-canvas(-muted/-sheet/-overlay)`, `bg-base(-hover/-pressed)`,
  `bg-muted*`, `bg-accent*`, `bg-interactive*`, `bg-error/-warning/-success*`,
  `bg-active*`, `bg-surface*`, `bg-white/-black/-disabled`, `bg-crypto-*`, `bg-discover-*`.
- Text: `text-base*`, `text-muted*`, `text-interactive*`, `text-error/-warning/-success`,
  `text-on-accent/-on-interactive/-on-error-strong/-on-warning/-on-success-strong`,
  `text-white/-black/-grey/-disabled/-active`.
- Borders: `border-base*`, `border-muted*`, `border-error/-warning/-success`,
  `border-focus/-active`, `border-black/-white/-disabled`.

**Size & spacing** — pixel-based scale (number = pixels, e.g. `p-16` = 16px, `h-64` = 64px).
- Sizes: `w-/h-/size-/min-/max-` with scale `1,2,4,6,8,10,12,16,20,24,32,40,48,64,80,96,112,128,144,160,176,208,224,256,320,400,480,560`.
- Spacing (`p/m/gap` + variants): `0,1,2,4,6,8,10,12,14,16,20,24,32,40,48,56,64,80,96,112,128,144,160,256`.

**Borders/shadows/gradients**: `rounded-sm/md/lg`, `border`/`border-2`,
`drop-shadow-sm..2xl`, `bg-gradient-top/-bottom/-{crypto}`.

**Discovery**: token/CSS-variable mappings live in
`node_modules/@ledgerhq/lumen-design-core/dist/lib/themes/**` (`css/` + `js/`) and
`.../dist/lib/utils/create*Plugin.js` (e.g. `createCustomPlugin.js`, `createPrimitivesPlugin.js`).

### Tailwind classname rules

- Never concatenate/interpolate class names. Always use complete strings.
- Valid: `className={cn("text-base", color && "bg-muted")}`
- Invalid: `` className={`text-${color}`} ``

### Icons

- Always import from `/symbols`: `import { ArrowRight } from '@ledgerhq/lumen-ui-react/symbols'`
- Use as component `<ArrowRight size={20} />` or prop `<Button icon={ArrowRight}>Label</Button>`
- Available sizes: 12, 16, 20, 24, 32, 40, 48, 56

### Compound components

Import parts together, e.g.:
`import { Select, SelectTrigger, SelectContent, SelectItem, SelectItemText } from '@ledgerhq/lumen-ui-react'`
`import { Dialog, DialogTrigger, DialogContent, DialogHeader } from '@ledgerhq/lumen-ui-react'`
`import { Tooltip, TooltipTrigger, TooltipContent } from '@ledgerhq/lumen-ui-react'`

### Dark mode

- Components support dark mode via CSS custom properties.
- Enable by adding `dark` class to a root/ancestor element. No component changes needed.

### Figma → Tailwind token mapping

Use only the unique part after the last hyphen of the CSS variable:
- `var(--background-base)` → `bg-base` (not `bg-background-base`)
- `var(--text-on-accent)` → `text-on-accent`
- `var(--border-muted)` → `border-muted`
- `var(--spacing-16)` → `p-16` / `m-16`
- `var(--radius-lg)` → `rounded-lg`
- `var(--border-width)` → `border`; `var(--border-width-active)` → `border-2`
- Typography comment `/* body/3 */` → `body-3`; `/* heading/2-semi-bold */` → `heading-2-semi-bold`

